{
  "text": "\u2022 Medication costs were assumed to be 71% of maintenance costs and were stratified by disease severity. 9,13 ( Table 2) \u2022 The rate of exacerbations by level of compliance was applied in the analysis. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Improvement in compliance had a direct effect (improvement) on the frequency of exacerbations.",
